data.title: Watch Ratatat's Short New Teaser for "Intro"
data.meta_description: Making Culture Pop. Find the latest entertainment news and the best in music, pop culture, sneakers, style and original shows.
data.text:
1.

The always mysterious Ratatat made a big comeback at this year’s Coachella, not only performing in California, but debuting a new single titled “Cream on Chrome” after a bit of a hiatus. Now only a month later, the group releases a short video for what may be the “Intro” off the upcoming album.

The clip shows Ratatat watering a cactus and peeling an orange in France, and after a short piano riff to start things off, those signature guitars come in and everything in life makes sense again.
